[recv] {"type": "turn_end", "message": {"role": "assistant", "content": [{"type": "thinking", "thinking": "**Exploring method dispatch**\n\nI’m thinking about how a superclass can get a public base method, but I’m not fully sure about the actual dispatch through that base method. If a method object from the superclass is invoked on a subclass, does that dynamic dispatch call the overridden implementation? It’s quite a bit to untangle! I wonder how reflection plays into this, especially when it comes to invoking those overridden methods. This back and forth is intriguing!", "thinkingSignature": "{\"id\":\"rs_03339c03f9f91d010169f4e0c42b60819d836d6035fa0552c6\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABp9ODeI8tVvupkGC2QePbkzpKpfkhNqM3pavZ9BAW886ZLUErryYrq_qoppdTMeh2ziDZTbZib9hUu78dQ42Oha9wYCMDgsxyF7vBe9XdOdQ57lErg3JFa5WfFCS33VwjBbSbwL-FAh-GzST7p3HMlpFnCjk9huTWWIXIOalzWi2H03LN91okQ1VIWGDY8SSVVwGkfBHuT7v9FjOjFS-S0QpDTqHReOh4ZRayqnuHC-pUKARGirl90Q_tNDOzqNYQulXuPzcP1Lco26PmrrbjOhSb0lj79X1O-Ao7y6EaV2J2tJIC-IWSg5PddC9HKSPB6w_9b8mI3lSsv3Aok6IWDcWkwb0zYSPNS1sIDoxqHtN4TyN4fQe6HWv6DTv4ez1ilFQUJqbC3R-54BZG_8SC00rjxPCuOeGnNg0dxcca8RKU3Bxk-8OKpKyLrvKmJ1zpt1iQ1TR_iz8Jwhwz0sFFLh6Wb5CO5R24KXTQLyHUzv6GxQZKVfLVr2a8S8icADntkaLeAxkBkX2Sb0M-bQPcAWKVCtNoQWBVCUqXJu8YGmhPq1LCfMPJAcgoy8w_W0pc1wjbxFszg_jlpXUXfaM3uVR65LnFcKVCku5Z7thYMOuGIvwrHIe03pU6NjiDvjw7gk0LfBMBIv1vSO2W1g-WS9svYT_UsetGkk1CKF5ee6P1V_tCRogI7JBK6L5nvTAAY-ocwToboyQz7_fE0jD8HmVoybADiKp2V9jN2wb-AqcufAzhyIRAzX63MqWR3dWDYjVUy5_wM4KConcMNMgvbXahMdEtBh4kAtuS1g49j7A_rKhpYVfRrOJ4X96E3jWgoEanSmy_N7PyZC-pWgsfl5zZa-BbRFNbopRg9ye8tS8f2rgTJv2sGARrpbomdOYxwz6O0Q34P1RIp_jY3OkJNEW-JJNuSoS2kAmUAis_6nw4teFljvwCvzkwfTGKM8IExjuv3IDN-OrSuPpjjYGvohlqQeBC8F-zYwwKxE5NiZy9Q0n8_GJ6LRJ0u9jU0Bnxy_sU0YdAjILj9J-FKOjH5bSZySHJeqR44gdmFMCmT-EIfSJCNB-tE9AT50UL6tU1Qbehy45gyoiKxU1OKL2PUJ9I0VamhUo08KLTOTvrgEcCMmZoHJ6tyrH7j3WCzUBJbRHcj7GoQv0dViyoQ7w__w88JbSMJKO9_T5dyz8ak3oL2MaEEUolNNShJ9v0W3d0WJBaBF0F3UeaRxCzcniN8wLoLlwPHUa3dGKk3_ELTB97QNWed7IiOrDs6X9cKP